20to%20the%20tariffs%2C%20but%20she%20had%20to%20pause%20her%20skin%20cleanser%20product.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHam%20learned%20valuable%20lessons%20about%20owning%20a%20business%20as%20she%20navigates%20a%20challenging%20launch%20period.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E30-year-old%20Irene%20Ham%20had%20just%20poured%20%2462%2C250%20of%20savings%20into%20inventory%20for%20her%20new%20Korean%20cosmetics%20brand%20when%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-liberation-day-reciprocal-tariffs-speech-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ELiberation%20Day%20tariffs%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20announced%20on%20April%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shipment%20had%20been%20ordered%20but%20hadn't%20arrived%20yet.%20She%20said%20her%20heart%20sank%20when%20she%20heard%20the%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20tariffs%20hit%2C%20it%20obviously%20was%20such%20an%20emotional%20piece%20of%20news%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Ham%2C%20who%20recently%20launched%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpoomcosmetics.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPoom%20Cosmetics%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20working%20on%20it%20for%20two%20years%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHam%20said%20she%20had%20ordered%20the%20bare%20minimum%20the%20South%20Korean%20factory%20would%20allow%20%E2%80%94%20and%20even%20that%20pushed%20her%20financial%20limits.%20Then%20came%20the%20news%20of%20a%2010%25%20baseline%20tariff%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhen-do-tariffs-start-trump-trade-plans-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E25%25%20%26quot%3Breciprocal%26quot%3B%20tariff%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20she%20said%20would%20have%20made%20it%20impossible%20for%20her%20to%20move%20forward%20with%20her%20business.%20Ham%20was%20facing%20the%20possibility%20of%20over%20%2421%2C000%20in%20added%20expenses%20for%20the%20inventory%20shipment%20from%20South%20Korea.%20On%20top%20of%20that%2C%20her%20product%20packaging%20was%20sourced%20from%20China%2C%20which%20was%20set%20to%20be%20affected%20by%20a%2054%25%20tariff%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20she%20paid%20customs%20before%20the%20tariffs%20went%20into%20effect%2C%20Ham%20avoided%20having%20to%20pay%20the%20tariffs%20on%20the%20South%20Korea%20shipment.%20However%2C%20she%20said%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-expect-us-china-trade-deal-next-90-days-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eongoing%20tariff%20uncertainty%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20led%20to%20setbacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20decided%20to%20pause%20launching%20a%20new%20face%20cleanser%20product%20line%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Bunforeseen%20costs%2C%26quot%3B%20though%20she%20had%20already%20finalized%20the%20formula%2C%20approved%20it%2C%20and%20completed%20the%20packaging%20design%20with%20her%20manufacturer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHam%20said%20she's%20been%20told%20she%20picked%20the%20%26quot%3Bworst%20time%26quot%3B%20to%20start%20a%20business.%20Along%20with%20tariffs%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-ban-details-when-how-legal-cases-trump-options%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elooming%20possibility%20of%20a%20TikTok%20ban%3C%2Fa%3E%20poses%20a%20threat%20to%20her%20marketing%20efforts%20as%20she's%20built%20a%20following%20on%20the%20app%20by%20documenting%20her%20entrepreneurial%20venture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20challenges%2C%20Ham%20said%20that%20after%20reading%20up%20about%20the%20tariffs%20and%20learning%20they%20could%20be%20used%20as%20a%20negotiation%20tactic%2C%20she%20realized%20the%20situation%20wasn't%20all%20doom%20and%20gloom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20if%20I%20started%20a%20business%20when%20it%20was%20all%20easy%2C%20everything%20was%20in%20my%20favor%2C%20then%20I%20don't%20think%20I%20would%20have%20the%20resilience%20to%20make%20it%20last%2C%26quot%3B%20Ham%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20a%20part%20of%20me%20is%20actually%20a%20little%20thankful%20that%20it's%20the%20worst%20time%20to%20start.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f05f7b6e-76bc-4635-a393-518f34af7ebc%5C%22%3EThe%20art%20of%20the%20pivot%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHam%20said%20she%20initially%20panicked%20about%20the%20newly%20announced%20tariff%20rates.%20But%20then%20she%20realized%20that%20she%20wouldn't%20necessarily%20have%20to%20raise%20her%20prices%20by%2025%25%20overall.%20The%20cost%20to%20manufacture%20her%20foundation%20would%20end%20up%20raising%20the%20price%20by%20%243%20or%20%244%20per%20bottle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3ESo%2C%20adding%20that%20to%20the%20price%20instead%20of%20making%20it%20a%20huge%20astronomical%20number%20increase%2C%26quot%3B%20Ham%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20was%20more%20manageable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHam%20also%20realized%20that%20she%20could%20survive%20without%20getting%20packaging%20materials%20like%20boxes%20and%20logo%20stickers%20from%20China%2C%20so%20she%20started%20looking%20into%20US-based%20suppliers%20like%20Uline%20and%20Sticker%20Mule%2C%20which%20didn't%20increase%20their%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20that%20meant%20her%20products%20don't%20look%20as%20refined%20or%20custom-made%20as%20originally%20planned%2C%20she%20said%20sacrifices%20were%20needed%20if%20she%20didn't%20want%20customers%20to%20pay%20even%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20even%20a%20perk%20from%20making%20the%20switch.%20Ham%20said%20the%20turnaround%20time%20is%20faster%2C%20and%20there's%20no%20bulk%20order%20requirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22faaa90bf-bfbf-4dc5-bb6b-6176c78bda5e%5C%22%3EGetting%20more%20confident%20in%20negotiating%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%20of%20navigating%20the%20tariff%20impact%2C%20Ham%20told%20BI%20that%20she's%20gained%20more%20confidence%20negotiating%20with%20manufacturers%2C%20particularly%20on%20the%20minimum%20order%20quantities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHam%20said%20some%20factories%20require%205%2C000%20