automate%20up%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.key4biz.it%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2FGlobal-Economics-Analyst_-The-Potentially-Large-Effects-of-Artificial-Intelligence-on-Economic-Growth-Briggs_Kodnani.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E44%25%20of%20legal%20tasks%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20forecast%20%26quot%3Bwas%20a%20shot%20in%20the%20arm%20to%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%26quot%3B%20Posner%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELegal%20tech%20used%20to%20be%20built%20by%20former%20lawyers%20solving%20problems%20they%20knew.%20It%20became%20a%20hotbed%20for%20talent%2C%20said%20Posner%2C%20attracting%20engineers%20eager%20to%20apply%20machine%20learning%20to%20legal%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20clients%20started%20knocking%20on%20the%20doors%20of%20law%20firms%2C%20asking%20how%20they%20were%20using%20the%20tech.%20They'd%20seen%20how%20AI%20was%20transforming%20operations%20inside%20their%20own%20companies%2C%20and%20they%20wanted%20assurance%20they%20were%20getting%20the%20best%20service%2C%20at%20the%20best%20rate%2C%20from%20their%20outside%20counsel.%20That%20pressure%20has%20pushed%20law%20firms%20to%20try%20to%20buy%20more%20advanced%20software%2C%20providing%20early%20and%20crucial%20revenue%20to%20legal-tech%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20the%20surge%20in%20funding%20has%20come%20a%20surge%20in%20sameness%3A%20startups%20built%20on%20slightly%20different%20combinations%20of%20the%20same%20foundation%20models%2C%20chasing%20the%20same%20broad%20promises.%20The%20technical%20moat%20is%20razor-thin%2C%20if%20it%20exists%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20phase%20of%20the%20boom%2C%20said%20Posner%2C%20will%20reward%20those%20who%20go%20deeper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPosner%20said%20he's%20most%20excited%20by%20startups%20building%20highly%20specialized%20tools%20aimed%20at%20narrow%20legal%20use%20cases.%20%26quot%3BThe%20moats%20are%20all%20the%20way%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20Posner%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20startups%20tackling%20precise%