.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fputin-made-mistake-sending-low-level-team-to-ukraine-talks-nato-chief%2Famp_articleshow%2F121209792.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fputin-made-mistake-sending-low-level-team-to-ukraine-talks-nato-chief%2Famp_articleshow%2F121209792.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fiverr's%20CEO%20tells%20BI%20he'll%20only%20hire%20candidates%20who%20use%20AI.%20Here's%20why.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224881%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Micha%20Kaufman%20Fiverr%20Ceo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6825d8b268a292900801630d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223254%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMicha%20Kaufman%20said%20that%20job%20hunters%20who%20aren't%20using%20AI%20will%20be%20left%20behind.%20%3Cp%3EFiverr%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMicha%20Kaufman%20told%20BI%20that%20AI%20use%20is%20now%20a%20baseline%20expectation%20at%20Fiverr.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPeople%20using%20AI%20will%20displace%20those%20who%20are%20not%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20freelance%20marketplace%20said.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFreelancers%20are%20ahead%20of%20the%20curve%2C%20often%20adopting%20AI%20tools%20faster%20than%20full-time%20employees%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20employers%2C%20AI%20skills%20are%20a%20nice-to-have.%20At%20Fiverr%2C%20they're%20non-negotiable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicha%20Kaufman%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20freelance%20marketplaces%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20he%20wouldn't%20hire%20anyone%20who%20isn't%20already%20using%20AI.%20Even%20candidates%20who%20say%20they're%20open%20to%20trying%20AI%2C%20but%20haven't%20actually%20used%20it%2C%20would%20be%20a%20red%20flag%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20wait%20to%20be%20taught%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20don't%20ensure%20that%20you%20sharpen%20your%20knives%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20be%20left%20behind.%20It's%20that%20simple.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20view%2C%20people%20who%20use%20AI%20to%20amplify%20their%20work%2C%20not%20just%20automate%20it%2C%20will%20set%20themselves%20apart%20in%20today's%20job%20market.%20The%20real%20competition%20isn't%20with%20the%20technology%20itself%2C%20he%20added%2C%20but%20with%20the%20people%20who%20embrace%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20less%20of%20a%20risk%20of%20technology%20displacing%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20think%20there's%20more%20risk%20of%20people%20who%20are%20very%20versed%20in%20technology%20displacing%20people%20who%20are%20not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d98e74ac-d2c2-4ff9-8e45-5127ce9a4462%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20'wake-up%20call'%20for%20everyone%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKaufman%20put%20forward%20this%20stance%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fmichakaufman%2Fstatus%2F1909610844008161380%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ememo%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Fiverr's%20775%20employees%20last%20month%2C%20warning%20that%20AI%20could%20threaten%20jobs%20at%20every%20level.%20%26quot%3BAI%20is%20coming%20for%20your%20jobs.%20Heck%2C%20it's%20coming%20for%20my%20job%20too.%20This%20is%20a%20wake-up%20call%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%2C%20later%20posting%20the%20message%20publicly%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20does%20not%20matter%20if%20you%20are%20a%20programmer%2C%20designer%2C%20product%20manager%2C%20data%20scientist%2C%20lawyer%2C%20customer%20support%20rep%2C%20salesperson%2C%20or%20a%20finance%20person%20-%20AI%20is%20coming%20for%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20BI%20the%20memo%20wasn't%20about%20creating%20fear%20but%20about%20facing%20reality.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20don't%20make%20that%20move%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20be%20out%20of%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%20%26quot%3BNot%20only%20in%20our%20company%20but%20also%20across%20the%20industry.%20There's%20not%20going%20to%20be%20a%20demand%20for%20people%20who%20are%20working%20like%20it%20was%20five%20years%20ago.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBefore%20it%20gets%20out%20somewhere%20else%2C%20this%20is%20an%20email%20I%20sent%20yesterday%20morning%20to%20my%20team.%20It%20applies%20equally%20to%20the%20freelance%C2%A0community%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FeLnFlJE9CZ%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FeLnFlJE9CZ%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Micha%20Kaufman%20(%40michakaufman)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmichakaufman%2Fstatus%2F1909610844008161380%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%208%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Fiverr%20CEO%20isn't%20alone%20in%20this%20philosophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fklarna-ceo-sebastian-siemiatkowski-ai-job-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EKlarna's%20CEO%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Sebastian%20Siemiatkowski%2C%20said%20in%20January%20that%20AI%20could%20do%20%26quot%3Ball%20our%20jobs%2C%20my%20own%20included%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20prospect%20he%20called%20%26quot%3Bgloomy%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20one%20he%20said%20the%20fintech%20had%20fully%20embraced.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20company%20reversed%20its%20AI%20hiring%20freeze%20to%20hire%20humans%20again.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Shopify%2C%20teams%20are%20now%20required%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshopify-ceo-tobi-lutke-employees-prove-ai-job-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edemonstrate%20that%20AI%