20it%20into%20the%20hospital.%20The%20nurses%20and%20doctors%20would%20eat%20my%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20practiced%20taking%20photos%20of%20the%20food%2C%20which%20I%20shared%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwest-coast-bakers-chefs-used-instagram-start-businesses-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20primarily%20on%20Instagram%20%E2%80%94%20on%20an%20account%20called%20Cooking%20with%20Cancer.%20It%20had%20very%20few%20followers%3A%20Most%20of%20them%20were%20nurses%2C%20doctors%2C%20family%20members.%20I%20would%20upload%20a%20really%20crappy%20picture%20of%20a%20cookie%2C%20and%20my%20followers%20would%20still%20be%20very%20supportive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22988561c1-d278-4b49-95cf-da17cda59cc4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'I%20think%20they're%20going%20to%20fire%20you'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20after%20an%20infusion%2C%20Sinclair%20representatives%20asked%20me%20for%20a%20meeting.%20My%20dad%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20they're%20going%20to%20fire%20you.%26quot%3B%20I%20thought%2C%20surely%20they%20couldn't%3B%20I%20had%20a%20contract%20with%20them%20that%20technically%20wasn't%20supposed%20to%20end%20until%20two%20years%20after%20my%20initial%20signing%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20couldn't%20fathom%20how%20it'd%20be%20possible%20to%20fire%20somebody%20on%20disability%20leave.%20When%20the%20HR%20person%20told%20me%20the%20news%20over%20the%20phone%2C%20I%20felt%20tears%20well%20up%20in%20my%20eyes%2C%20and%20all%20I%20remember%20saying%20out%20loud%20was%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20still%20in%20treatment.%26quot%3B%20There%20was%20silence%20on%20the%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(Editor's%20note%3A%20George's%20former%20station%2C%20WTVC%2C%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20BI's%20requests%20for%20comment.%20A%20Sinclair%20representative%20did%20not%20reply%20to%20BI's%20questions%20and%20said%20the%20station's%20leadership%20from%20that%20time%20is%20no%20longer%20