om%2Ffacebooks-veteran-jay-parikh-is-stepping-down-2020-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJay%20Parikh%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%26quot%3Btenant%26quot%3B%20is%20the%20term%20used%20to%20describe%20corporate%20users%20of%20the%20Microsoft%20365%20suite%20of%20business%20applications.%20A%20Copilot%20that%20has%20access%20to%20these%20tenants%20would%20essentially%20be%20able%20to%20access%20customer%20information%20stored%20within%20their%20Microsoft%20365%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParikh%20explained%20in%20the%20email%20that%20Microsoft%20is%20using%20different%20AI%20techniques%20to%20power%20the%20Tenant%20Copilot%20feature.%20Supervised%20fine-tuning%20helps%20%26quot%3Bto%20capture%20a%20tenant's%20voice.%26quot%3B%20The%20tool%20will%20also%20tap%20into%20OpenAI's%20o3%20reasoning%20model%20%26quot%3Bto%20shape%20its%20thought%20process.%26quot%3B%20Lastly%2C%20%26quot%3Bagentic%26quot%3B%20fine-tuning%20will%20%26quot%3Bempower%20real-world%20tasks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20at%20the%20time%20planned%20to%20offer%20a%20public%20preview%20of%20Tenant%20Copilot%20at%20Build%2C%20according%20to%20the%20memo.%20The%20company%20sometimes%20changes%20what%20it%20plans%20to%20announce%20at%20the%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20CoreAI%20Applied%20Engineering%20team%20is%20also%20%26quot%3Bworking%20to%20launch%20a%20collaborative%20go-to-market%20plan%20for%20top-tier%20customers%20to%20drive%20successful%20adoption%20of%20our%20Al%20cloud%2C%26quot%3B%20Parikh%20added%20in%20the%20memo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bca5ebd3-066b-4042-9052-c00565cbaf64%5C%22%3EParikh's%20'Agent%20Factory'%20concept%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EParikh%20is%20the%20former%20head%20of%20engineering%20at%20Facebook.%20Microsoft%20CEO%20Satya%20Nadella%20hired%20Parikh%20in%20October%20and%20tapped%20him%20in%20January%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-ai-group-under-jay-parikh-former-facebook-head-engineering-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erun%20a%20new%20group%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20CoreAI%20Platform%20and%20Tools%20focused%20on%20building%20AI%20tools.%20The%20group%20combined%20Microsoft's%20developer%20division%20and%20AI%20platform%20team%20and%20is%20responsible%20for%20GitHub%20Copilot%2C%20Microsoft's%20AI-powered%20coding%20assistant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year's%20Build%20event%20will%20be%20Parikh's%20first%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20this%20new%20organization.%20In%20the%20email%20to%20the%20nearly%2010%2C000%20employees%20in%20the%20organization%2C%20Parikh%20discussed%20a%20new%20%26quot%3BAgent%20Factory%26quot%3B%20concept.%20That's%20likely%20a%20nod%20to%20cofounder%20Bill%20Gates%2C%20who%20talked%20about%20Microsoft%20being%20a%20%26quot%3Bsoftware%20factory.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBuilding%20our%20vision%20demands%20this%20type%20of%20culture%20%E2%80%94%20one%20where%20Al%20is%20embedded%20in%20how%20we%20think%2C%20design%2C%20and%20deliver%2C%26quot%3B%20Parikh%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Agent%20Factory%20reflects%20this%20shift%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20in%20what%20we%20build%2C%20but%20in%20how%20we%20build%20it%20together.%20If%20we%20want%20every%20developer%20(and%20everyone)%20to%20shape%20the%20future%2C%20we%20have%20to%20get%20there%20first.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParikh%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20work%20across%20organizations%20to%20collaborate%20on%20AI%20agents%2C%20through%20a%20%26quot%3Bnew%20type%20of%20cross-product%20review%26quot%3B%20combining%20teams%20such%20as%20security%20services%20like%20Entra%20and%20Intune%20with%20%26quot%3Bhigh-ambition%20agent%20efforts%26quot%3B%20within%20LinkedIn%2C%20Dynamics%2C%20and%20Microsoft%20365.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224e1aa6f3-3146-47e4-bec2-1cd10c0331f1%5C%22%3EMeet%20your%20new%20AI%20agent%20co-worker%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20this%20effort%20focuses%20on%20how%20to%20manage%20AI%20agents%20alongside%20human%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%2C%20for%20example%2C%20has%20been%20working%20on%20how%20to%20handle%20identity%20management%20for%20AI%20agents%2C%20according%20to%20the%20memo.%20This%20technology%20usually%20controls%20security%20access%20for%20human%20users.%20Now%2C%20the%20company%20is%20trying%20to%20spin%20up%20a%20similar%20system%20for%20AI%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20hypothesis%20is%20that%20all%20agent%20identities%20will%20reside%20in%20Entra%2C%26quot%3B%20Parikh%20wrote%2C%20although%20%26quot%3Bnot%20every%20agent%20will%20require%20an%20identity%20(some%20simpler%20agents%20in%20M365%20or%20Studio%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20don't%20need%20one).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20is%20taking%20a%20similar%20approach%20to%20M365%20Admin%20Center%2C%20which%20is%20used%20by%20IT%20administrators%20to%20manage%20employee%20access%20to%20applications%2C%20data%2C%20devices%2C%20and%20users.%20Future%20versions%20of%20this%20system%20will%20accommodate%20AI%20agents%20as%20%26quot%3Bdigital%20teammates%26quot%3B%20of%20human%20workers%2C%20according%20to%20Parikh's%20memo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft's%20Copilot%20Analytics%20service%20is%20also%20expanding%20into%20broader%20workforce%20analytics%20to%20give%20corporate%20customers%20a%20view%20of%20how%20work%20gets%20done%20both%20by%20humans%20and%20AI%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Parikh%20aims%20to%20make%20Azure%20AI%20Foundry%2C%20its%20generative%20AI%20development%20hub%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20single%20platform%20for%20the%20agentic%20applications%20that%20you%20build%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BAt%20Build%2C%20we%20will%20have%20the%20early%20versions%20of%20this%2C%20and%20we'll%20iterate%20quickly%20to%20tackle%20a%20variety%20of%20customer%20use%20cases.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aastewart%40b