3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclawed%20back%20its%20losses%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20in%20the%20green%20for%20the%20year.%20That%20means%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-trump-buy-tweets-truth-social-trade-war-tariffs-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump%3C%2Fa%3E's%20Truth%20Social%20fans%20who%20followed%20his%20%26quot%3BTHIS%20IS%20A%20GREAT%20TIME%20TO%20BUY!!!%26quot%3B%20advice%20are%20looking%20pretty%20smug%2C%20while%20panic%20sellers%20are%20likely%20feeling%20pretty%20regretful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22295f991d-6154-404c-a40a-c059795f9b35%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPanic%20selling%20is%20more%20likely%20than%20you%20think%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPanic%20selling%20isn't%20always%20a%20rookie%20mistake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20when%20people%20do%20hold%20on%20to%20their%20assets%2C%20it's%20not%20exactly%20a%20popular%20decision%20in%20the%20moment.%20Brian%20Belski%2C%20BMO's%20chief%20investment%20officer%2C%20stayed%20steadfast%20through%20the%20market%20noise%20but%20received%20a%20hefty%20dose%20of%20criticism%20for%20doing%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20took%20a%20lot%20of%20heat%20in%20the%20media%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20heat%20internally%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20heat%20from%20our%20clients%2C%26quot%3B%20Belski%20said%20on%20a%20May%2013%20episode%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BBloomberg%20Surveillance%26quot%3B%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20making%20binary%20decisions%20based%20on%20emotion%20without%20analysis.%20And%20the%20analysis%20said%20that%20the%20markets%20were%20not%20going%20to%20be%20as%20broken%20as%20everybody%20thought.%20And%20I%20think%20everyone%20was%2C%20once%20again%2C%20jumping%20to%20conclusions%2C%26quot%3B%20Belski%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22672c89b1-cd46-4ed0-8626-789d1b94286f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20math%20behind%20panic%20selling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMarket%20timing%20is%20futile%20and%20staying%20invested%20is%20paramount%2C%26quot%3B%20Jacob%20Manoukian%2C%20JPMorgan%20Private%20Bank's%20US%20head%20of%20investment%20strategy%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20recent%20note.%20%26quot%3BOver%20the%20last%2020%20years%2C%20seven%20of%20the%2010%20best%20days%20in%20markets%20occurred%20within%2015%20days%20of%20the%2010%20worst%20days.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPut%20simply%2C%20some%20of%20the%20best-performing%20stock%20market%20days%20come%20after%20the%20biggest%20declines.%20If%20you%20pull%20your%20funds%20out%20of%20the%20market%20during%20a%20drawdown%2C%20you%20not%20only%20sell%20your%20assets%20at%20a%20loss%2C%20but%20you%20also%20miss%20out%20on%20the%20recoveries%20that%20happen%20afterward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Adam's%20case%2C%20he%20cashed%20out%20of%20TSMC%20and%20Nvidia%20at%20%24185%20and%20%24119%20per%20share%2C%20respectively%2C%20according%20to%20trade%20confirmation%20documents%20viewed%20by%20Business%20Insider.%20As%20of%20May%2015%2C%20shares%20of%20TSMC%20were%20trading%20at%20around%20%24194%2C%20and%20shares%20of%20Nvidia%20were%20at%20%24135%2C%20which%20means%20he%20missed%20out%20on%20roughly%205%25%20and%2013%25%20gains%20on%20those%20stocks%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BObviously%2C%20it%20doesn't%20feel%20great%20to%20sell%20and%20miss%20out%20on%20future%20gains%2C%26quot%3B%20Adam%20said.%20He's%20also%20frustrated%20with%20Trump's%20aggressive%20tariff%20messaging%20that%20rocked%20the%20market%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20having%20trouble%20putting%20my%20trust%20in%20the%20stock%20market%20right%20now%20because%20of%20what's%20going%20on%20with%20tariffs%20and%20what%20seems%20like%20stock%20manipulation%20based%20on%20the%20actions%20of%20our%20current%20administration%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228a6b26e7-4395-4b0b-8d1f-863f5991612e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20now%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20panic%20sell%26quot%3B%20seems%20like%20basic%20advice%2C%20yet%20every%20time%20a%20market%20drawdown%20occurs%2C%20investors%20still%20run%20for%20the%20hills.%20Since%201954%2C%20a%20correction%20of%2020%25%20or%20more%20has%20occurred%20about%20once%20every%20six%20years%2C%20according%20to%20Capital%20Group.%20So%20why%20haven't%20retail%20and%20institutional%20investors%20alike%20learned%20their%20lesson%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20get%20caught%20up%20in%20their%20emotions%20more%20often%20than%20they'd%20like%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-tips-how-to-start-investing-trade-war-trump-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKatie%20Klingensmith%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20chief%20investment%20strategist%20at%20Edelman%20Financial%20Engines.%20No%20two%20market%20sell-offs%20are%20alike%2C%20either.%20The%20policy-induced%20market%20sell-off%20of%20the%20last%20few%20months%20looks%20quite%20different%20from%20the%20pandemic%20crash%20of%202020.%20And%20sometimes%2C%20newer%20investors%20just%20haven't%20lived%20through%20the%20jarring%20reality%20of%20seeing%20their%20holdings%20plunge%2020%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20the%20antidote%20to%20panic%20selling%3F%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuy-invest-in-stocks-now-market-volatility-trump-tariff-uncertainty-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EYou%20buy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Belski%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20you%20try%20not%20to%20outsmart%20yourself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20to%20stay%20invested%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fdollar-cost-averaging%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edollar-cost%20averaging%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20buying%20back%20into%20the%20market%20at%20regular%20intervals%20can%20help%20smooth%20out%20volatility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20found%20yourself%20panic%20selling%2C%20that%20also%20might%20be%20a%20sign%20to%20reassess%20your%20risk%2