-could-unravel-medicaid-expansion-in-12-states%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esome%20commentators%20expected%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20GOP%20committee%20members%20opted%20not%20to%20lower%20the%20federal%20Medicaid%20matching%20rate%20or%20implement%20a%20per%20capita%20spending%20cap%2C%20which%20were%20pushed%20for%20by%20some%20GOP%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepublicans%20have%20been%20split%20on%20the%20best%20path%20forward%20for%20Medicaid%20cuts%2C%20as%20some%20represent%20districts%20that%20have%20among%20the%20highest%20Medicaid%20reliance%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20Trump's%20big%2C%20beautiful%20bill%20is%20far%20from%20a%20guarantee.%20The%20coming%20weeks%20and%20potentially%20months%20of%20negotiations%20likely%20mean%20that%20the%20final%20iteration%20will%20reflect%20what%20Republicans%20can%20agree%20on%20cutting.%20For%20now%2C%20though%2C%20Medicaid%20seems%20to%20be%20in%20their%20crosshairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20potential%20Medicaid%20cuts%3F%20Contact%20these%20reporters%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ansheidlower%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ensheidlower%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajkaplan%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ejkaplan%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouse-gop-proposes-medicaid-cuts-would-impact-kids-lower-earners-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747384202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6824f5de3fe8d3928365de6d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouse-gop-proposes-medicaid-cuts-would-impact-kids-lower-earners-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Republic