%80%9C%3Cem%3EWhile%20taking%20care%20of%20my%20baby%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20bring%20in%20emotions%2C%20and%20I%20had%20a%20to-do%20list%20in%20my%20mind%20and%20struck%20off%20things%20as%20I%20finished%20them.%20I%20never%20thought%20about%20myself.%20It%20was%20always%20the%20baby.%20I%20think%20mothers%20just%20power%20through%20everything%2C%20small%20or%20big%20challenges%2C%20after%20they%20give%20birth%20to%20their%20baby.%20The%20secret%20is%20to%20just%20go%20with%20the%20flow%20and%20not%20think%20much%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20with%20raw%20honesty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20daily%20life%20a%20little%20more%20manageable%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20bring%20in%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ESo%20as%20to%20ease%20the%20daily%20duties%20as%20a%20mother%2C%20we%20hired%20a%20help%2C%20to%20bathe%20and%20massage%20the%20baby%2C%20wash%20her%20clothes%20and%20more.%20For%20other%20tasks%20of%20playing%20with%20her%20or%20reading%20her%20a%20book%20we%20have%20my%20parents%20and%20in-laws%20around%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20routines%2C%20Priyanka%20has%20let%20go%20of%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20strict%20schedule%20%E2%80%94%20something%20she%20once%20held%20close.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EI%20just%20know%20what%20I%20have%20to%20finish%20during%20the%20day.%20There%20is%20no%20timing%20set%20for%20any%20of%20the%20tasks.%20I%20was%20someone%20who%20had%20a%20schedule%20for%20everything%20but%20now%20I%20have%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20not%20having%20a%20schedule%20and%20that%20it%20is%20all%20about%20the%20baby%E2%80%99s%20demands.%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20just%20three%20months%2C%20this%20new%20mother%20has%20learned%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20lessons%20of%20all%20%E2%80%94%20that%20motherhood%20rarely%20goes%20by%20the%20book.%20And%20sometimes%2C%20the%20best%20way%20to%20show%20up%20is%20simply%20to%20flow%20with%20the%20chaos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3